This repository contains the data and code to replicate the results in [Production Rigidity, Input Lumpiness, Efficiency, and the Technological Hurdle of Quebec Dairy Farms](https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/full/10.1111/cjag.12156) published in the Canadian Journal of Agricultural Economics. 

The results in the paper were produced using Stata. The Stata file `Rigidity_lumpiness_efficiency_hurdle.do` contains the code to generate the results in the paper. 

The file `Replication of Larue, Pouliot & Singbo (2017).Rmd` reproduces the results in the paper using R. The file also generates the figures in the paper that were produced using R and prepares the data for estimation. 
